{
  "stem": "13258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Guttmann, I-- don't go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Stay in the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I will be back in half an hour.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I take you with me in my car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I don't know what his real name was, but his name was Polanski.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we sat down in the station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And about half an hour, the stationmaster comes out and says, is a Dr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Guttmann here?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, we just had a telephone call from the gentleman who talked to you on the road.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "His orders have changed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He is not coming back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we hopped on the next train which came, which was so full.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were those European-style, express-train cars, with a corridor and compartments inside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, we got pressed into the toilet at the end of the corridor and rode with the window open, three or four people standing [LAUGHS] in that toilet until we came to the city of Lemberg in Austria-- it was called.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Polish, it was Lwow, L-W-O-W.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "L-W-O-W.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And now in Ukrainians call it Lwiw, L-W-I-W.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stopped at the outskirts of the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the first thing that we saw, there was a flour mill-- [NON-ENGLISH] I think it was called-- in flames.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was burned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Went into the city, and there were constantly air alarms, air alerts, in the house, and, and hide.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father went to visit a rabbi, who, at one time, had been a rabbi in our city.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was very non-committal and would not say much to my father and neither help nor nothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we went-- first of all, being hungry, in the-- found the Jewish restaurant and had something to eat there.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
